      <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Your name" autocomplete="name"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#191817; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
      <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="Email address" autocomplete="email"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#191817; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
    </div>
    <input type="text" name="property_address" required placeholder="Your Stafford address (street + number)"
      style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#191817; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
    <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <button type="submit"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.78rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#b98229; color:#191817; padding:0.75rem 1.75rem; border:none; cursor:pointer; white-space:nowrap;border-radius:8px;">
        Request My Free Appraisal
      </button>
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:300; color:#78716c; margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Daniel will be in touch promptly. No pressure.</p>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>
<style>
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .suburb-form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>
<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I work the inner north corridor regularly and know how Stafford fits into the buyer decision. Many buyers arrive in Stafford after doing serious comparisons against Gordon Park, Lutwyche and Kedron and deciding that the price differential is no longer justified. What they find is a suburb with genuine land content, leafy internal streets, and a community feel that reflects decades of stable owner-occupation. That is a set of fundamentals that supports consistent buyer demand from families who want the inner north without the premium postcode price tag.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Stafford Road gives the suburb strong bus connectivity to the CBD, and Stafford City Shopping Centre at the northern end of the suburb provides practical everyday retail without requiring a car trip. Gympie Road forms the eastern boundary and connects quickly to the inner ring. The housing mix runs from original post-war timber homes on generous blocks through to a growing number of renovated properties, with the best-performing pockets sitting on the quiet residential streets away from the main arterials where block sizes are more generous and the streetscape is established and leafy.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Stafford Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner North Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Owner-Occupier Suburb</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Family demand, good fundamentals</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/gordon-park" style="color:#b98229;">Gordon Park</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kedron" style="color:#b98229;">Kedron</a>, <a href="/suburbs/lutwyche" style="color:#b98229;">Lutwyche</a>, <a href="/suburbs/albion" style="color:#b98229;">Albion</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

